gText_Birch_Welcome:: @ 82C897B
	.string "Ello!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the world of Cranbrook!\p"
	.string "My name is Dr. Reynolds.\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon:: @ 82C89FB
	.string "This is what we call a “POKéMON.”\p"
	.string "But you already know that.\n"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech:: @ 82C8A1F
	.string "Here at CRANBROOK we use POKéMON,\n"
	.string "as our slaves. Holding them captive, and\l"
	.string "making them bend over to our\l"
	.string "every whim and desire\p"
	.string "And sometimes, we like to make them\n"
	.string "battle each other for fun.\p"
	.string "Despite my expertise, I don't\n"
	.string "own every POKéMON.\p"
	.string "In fact, I've been undertaking research,\n"
	.string "to try and capture them all and,\l"
	.string "rule CRANBROOK with an iron fist.\n"
	.string "Anyway, that's enough about me.\p"
	.string "$"

